Follow this: http://tecadmin.net/install-nagios-core-service-on-centos-rhel/#

Install CentOS nagios Linux client:
------------------------------------------

enable epel repo

yum install nrpe -y

edit /etc/nagios/nrpe.cfg

allowed_hosts=127.0.0.1
to
allowed_hsots=127.0.0.1,10.128.0.2
<10.128.0.2> that is my nagios server IP

systemctl restart nrpe

From Server:
/usr/local/nagios/libexec/check_nrpe -H 10.128.0.3

O/P expected is 

NRPE v2.15

